    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
思はずも筆はしり<lb />
忽ちに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">画</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は成りぬ。<lb />
この時に涙ぞくだる。われながら<lb />
芸の力に泣きぬるか。<lb />
<lb />
<span rend="sesame_dot" rendition="em">き</span>と見れば、あさましや、<lb />
をののきに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">眼</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">め</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぞ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">眩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>む。<lb />
むくつけき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">斑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まだら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">獣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けもの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>尾を曳きて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">面</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>には君をゑがきたり。<lb />
<lb />
やがて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">画</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は炉の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">中</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
燃えながら且つ泣きぬ。<lb />
ああされど、偽らざりき、わが心<lb />
思ふはげにも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">然</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なりける。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
